                    "company": "art",
                    "description": "I work in a variety of media and make (cut) photos, textile sculptures and installations, drawings, animations and texts. \n\nMy work is centered round the different manifestations of \u2018the self\u2019, in which physical, mental, emotional and social aspects overlap and contradict. The \u2018I\u2019 becomes manifest in relation to \u2018the other\u2019 through posture \u2013 garments \u2013 language \u2013 sign and all these aspects appear in my work.\n\nCollaboration is an important element in my practice, both as member of Foundation B.a.d (from 1993) and in other projects. Writer and lecturer at various academies in the Netherlands and Belgium, I am currently based as JobCoach for Fine Art at the Willem de Kooning Academie in Rotterdam.",
